\import{table-macros}
\title{FMOz 2026}
\author{liamoc}
\date{2026-06-05}
\p{This week I attended (along with many others from ANU including [[hoefner]], [[alinosher]], [[xinloi]], [[kaiphan]] and [[carloz]]) the yearly meeting of Formal Methods researchers in Australia at the [[uq]]. It was good to hear from colleagues again, and I was very impressed by the size of the group.}
